    <briefdescription>
<para>Maps scenes to their associated viewports for rendering. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1modules_1_1scene_1_1types_1_1SceneToViewportMap" kindref="compound">SceneToViewportMap</ref> maintains the relationship between Scene objects and Viewport objects. A scene can be rendered through multiple viewports (e.g., split-screen), and a viewport renders exactly one scene (1:N).</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para>SceneRenderingSystem </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para>Scene </para>
</simplesect>
